VALUES
  ('optician-moex-01769', 'optician', 'optician-moex-108-d6d7f3e6', 'sub-optician-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '有關針孔（pinhole）的敘述，下列何者錯誤？', '["針孔試驗是用來檢測，是否能用眼鏡鏡片來改善患者視力的方法", "當針孔試驗無法改善視力，顯示患者可能是因其他病理因素而影響視力", "瞳孔直徑較大的人會比瞳孔直徑較小的人更能忍受度數矯正不足", "模糊盤（blur disc）的直徑對於字母來說相對大時，字母的影像較不易辨認"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:35+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "8df8b65115b1", "answer_pdf_sha1": "d875f69b2637", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "108110", "c": "113", "s": "1109", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "眼鏡光學概要", "year": "108", "exam_name": "108年第二次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試、108年專技人員高等考試法醫師、語言治療師、聽力...", "original_question_number": 1, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optician", "db_exam_id": "optician"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('optician-moex-01770', 'optician', 'optician-moex-108-d6d7f3e6', 'sub-optician-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '有關眼鏡放大率及矯正的視網膜影像之敘述，下列何者錯誤？', '["矯正的視網膜像與基本的視網膜像大小相比，負鏡片會放大，正鏡片會縮小", "隱形眼鏡不會將未矯正眼的視網膜像大小改變太多", "非球面鏡的優點之一是有較小的眼鏡放大率", "當從一般眼鏡改換為隱形眼鏡後，近視的視網膜像會變大，遠視的視網膜像會變小"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:35+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "8df8b65115b1", "answer_pdf_sha1": "d875f69b2637", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "108110", "c": "113", "s": "1109", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "眼鏡光學概要", "year": "108", "exam_name": "108年第二次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試、108年專技人員高等考試法醫師、語言治療師、聽力...", "original_question_number": 2, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optician", "db_exam_id": "optician"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('optician-moex-01771', 'optician', 'optician-moex-108-d6d7f3e6', 'sub-optician-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '正視眼的白內障患者經手術摘除水晶體後，若未植入人工水晶體，稱為無水晶體症。此時的高度屈光不 正可用何種透鏡矯正？', '["平面鏡", "凹透鏡", "凸透鏡", "圓柱透鏡"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:35+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "8df8b65115b1", "answer_pdf_sha1": "d875f69b2637", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "108110", "c": "113", "s": "1109", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "眼鏡光學概要", "year": "108", "exam_name": "108年第二次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試、108年專技人員高等考試法醫師、語言治療師、聽力...", "original_question_number": 3, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optician", "db_exam_id": "optician"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('optician-moex-01772', 'optician', 'optician-moex-108-d6d7f3e6', 'sub-optician-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '當患者配戴上自己的雙焦點眼鏡可以看清楚的範圍是33 cm到1 m，其總景深為±0.5 D，他實際調節力為 多少？', '["1 D", "1.5 D", "2 D", "3 D"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:35+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "8df8b65115b1", "answer_pdf_sha1": "d875f69b2637", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "108110", "c": "113", "s": "1109", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "眼鏡光學概要", "year": "108", "exam_name": "108年第二次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試、108年專技人員高等考試法醫師、語言治療師、聽力...", "original_question_number": 4, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optician", "db_exam_id": "optician"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('optician-moex-01773', 'optician', 'optician-moex-108-d6d7f3e6', 'sub-optician-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '遠視患者以正透鏡矯正後視力為 1.0，若持續加入正透鏡至患者可以維持最佳視力的度數為止，此時所增 加的正透鏡度數為下列何者？', '["機能遠視度數（facultative hyperopia）", "絕對遠視度數（absolute hyperopia）", "顯性遠視度數（manifest hyperopia）", "調節幅度（amplitude of accommodation）"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:35+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "8df8b65115b1", "answer_pdf_sha1": "d875f69b2637", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "108110", "c": "113", "s": "1109", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "眼鏡光學概要", "year": "108", "exam_name": "108年第二次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試、108年專技人員高等考試法醫師、語言治療師、聽力...", "original_question_number": 5, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optician", "db_exam_id": "optician"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('optician-moex-01774', 'optician', 'optician-moex-108-d6d7f3e6', 'sub-optician-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '用-8.00 DS的球面眼鏡可以完全矯正李先生的左眼，若要換戴隱形眼鏡，應用多少度數才有相同的矯正效 果？設頂點距離（vertex distance）為12 mm。', '["-8.00 D", "-7.25 D", "-6.50 D", "-8.75 D"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:35+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "8df8b65115b1", "answer_pdf_sha1": "d875f69b2637", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "108110", "c": "113", "s": "1109", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "眼鏡光學概要", "year": "108", "exam_name": "108年第二次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試、108年專技人員高等考試法醫師、語言治療師、聽力...", "original_question_number": 6, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optician", "db_exam_id": "optician"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('optician-moex-01775', 'optician', 'optician-moex-108-d6d7f3e6', 'sub-optician-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '增加頂點距離的長度時，透鏡要如何處理，才會有相同矯正效果？①增加凸透鏡的度數  ②增加凹透鏡', '["減少凹透鏡的度數", "減少凸透鏡的度數", "", ""]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:35+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "8df8b65115b1", "answer_pdf_sha1": "d875f69b2637", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "108110", "c": "113", "s": "1109", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "眼鏡光學概要", "year": "108", "exam_name": "108年第二次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試、108年專技人員高等考試法醫師、語言治療師、聽力...", "original_question_number": 7, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["incomplete_options"], "slug": "optician", "db_exam_id": "optician"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('optician-moex-01776', 'optician', 'optician-moex-108-d6d7f3e6', 'sub-optician-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '當史耐倫視力表（Snellen chart）為0.5（20/40或6/12），等於最小分辨角對數（logMAR）視力值約多少？', '["-0.3", "0.3", "-0.5", "0.5"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:35+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "8df8b65115b1", "answer_pdf_sha1": "d875f69b2637", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "108110", "c": "113", "s": "1109", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "眼鏡光學概要", "year": "108", "exam_name": "108年第二次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試、108年專技人員高等考試法醫師、語言治療師、聽力...", "original_question_number": 8, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optician", "db_exam_id": "optician"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('optician-moex-01777', 'optician', 'optician-moex-108-d6d7f3e6', 'sub-optician-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '一眼度數為plano/-3.00D×180，在未矯正的情況下觀看6 m遠的散光盤（astigmatic dial），看到的情況 如何？', '["水平與垂直線條均模糊，但水平線條更模糊", "水平與垂直線條均模糊，但垂直線條更模糊", "垂直線條最清晰，水平線條最模糊", "水平線條最清晰，垂直線條最模糊"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:35+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "8df8b65115b1", "answer_pdf_sha1": "d875f69b2637", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "108110", "c": "113", "s": "1109", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "眼鏡光學概要", "year": "108", "exam_name": "108年第二次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試、108年專技人員高等考試法醫師、語言治療師、聽力...", "original_question_number": 9, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optician", "db_exam_id": "optician"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('optician-moex-01778', 'optician', 'optician-moex-108-d6d7f3e6', 'sub-optician-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列何者是臨床上最適合不規則散光（irregular astigmatism）的處置方式？', '["框架眼鏡", "硬式隱形眼鏡", "屈光雷射手術", "水晶體植入"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:35+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "8df8b65115b1", "answer_pdf_sha1": "d875f69b2637", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "108110", "c": "113", "s": "1109", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "眼鏡光學概要", "year": "108", "exam_name": "108年第二次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試、108年專技人員高等考試法醫師、語言治療師、聽力...", "original_question_number": 10, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optician", "db_exam_id": "optician"}'::jsonb, NULL)
